The script automatically synchronizes and displays XBMC library.

Requirements:
- Server with Apache server, PHP 5, MySql 5
- Addon "Movielib" for XBMC https://raw.github.com/Regss/xbmc-regss-repository/master/repo/repository.regss/repository.regss-1.2.1.zip 

Default passwords:
Access to site: user
Access to admin panel: admin

Movielib XBMC Add-on repository:
https://raw.github.com/Regss/xbmc-regss-repository/master/repo/repository.regss/repository.regss-1.2.1.zip

In Panel Admin section you need to generate token and put it to addon settings with URL to script.